This page describes ways to determine the [EmacsSyntaxTable syntax] at the current position in the buffer.

== Investigate the font-lock face ==

One approach, if using [EnablingFontLock Font Lock Mode], is to check the ##face## property at point. For instance, comments can commonly be identified as having the ##font-lock-comment-face##:

    (eq (get-text-property (point) 'face)
        'font-lock-comment-face)
